title: Ghostbusters 1975 Live Action
description:
Ghostbusters 1975 Live Action


Two guys and their pet gorilla hunt spooks.
A live-action children's show, the Ghost Busters travel around the globe looking for ghosts. They dispel the ghosts with a weird camera-looking gadget. 


"Spenser and Kong are a pair of bumbling spook chasers who use their "ghost dematerializer" ray in an attempt to battle the spirits of notorious villains. Assisting Spenser and Kong in their mission is Tracy, an intelligent gorilla. Every episode opens with a parody of "Mission: Impossible" in which Spenser, Tracy & Kong are blown up by an exploding tape recorder."

 Forrest Tucker, Larry Storch, Bob Burns
